bdd_project/
├── features/
│   ├── user_login.feature
│   ├── other_feature.feature
│   └── ...
├── steps/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── user_login_steps.py
│   └── other_steps.py
├── pages/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── login_page.py
│   └── dashboard_page.py
├── behave.ini
├── driver.py
├── environment.py
└── requirements.txt



https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/login
Pt a rula un proiect BDD folosim comanda behave in consola
    behave
    behave --tags=valid_login
    behave -f html --tags=valid_login -o valid_login_report.html
     behave -f html -o full_login_report.html
Structura de executie
1.Feature files ( Fiecare pas din fiecare scenariu )
2.Step files ( se exectuta metoda step impl pt fiecare pas )
3.Pages files ( apelam metodele in pages prin variabila context)
(4) Step files se executa assert-urile

Git -- > github

1. Creem un repozitoriu in remote ( github)
2. Urmam instructiunile din repozitoriul remote pt  urca codul din local
    echo "# login-BDD" >> README.md
    git init
    git add README.md
    git commit -m "first commit"
    git branch -M main
    git remote add origin https://github.com/PaulLoghin/login-BDD.git
    git push -u origin main




